    | This Privacy Policy (“Policy”) describes how your personal information is collected, used, and disclosed by Forage Co. and its related companies (“Chowpocket” or “We” or “Us”).

  p
    | Policy applies to the Chowpocket websites available at www.chowpocket.com or any of our other websites that post this Policy (the “Site”) and our online services (the “Services”). 

  p 
