  p
    | When you make payments on our Site, our third party payment processor will collect all information necessary to complete the transaction, including your name, credit card number and billing address.
  p
    | When you transmit your payment information to our third party payment processor, the personal information you upload, including your credit card number, name, and address will be transmitted to our payment processor in an encrypted format via Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) technology.
  p
